newsitem.title: NETHERLANDS: European feeds remain dull in afternoon.
newsitem.headline: European feeds remain dull in afternoon.

text.p: The European meals and feeds market remained quietly this afternoon with only two nearby tapioca trades reported, market sources said.
"The firmer seller prices and a stronger dollar kept most buyers sidelined ahead of the weekend. A weaker Chicago soymeal futures opening also kept a lid on activity," one broker said.
Spot Thai hard tapioca pellets traded at 19 marks per 100 kg fob Weser and at 19.75 fob Ghent.--KAREL LUIMES +31 20 504 5832
